	<Title>
		Wheezing in children: Could it be asthma?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Wheezing in children may be a sign of asthma &amp;mdash; but not always.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		My 11-month-old son has had several wheezing episodes recently. Does this mean he has asthma?
	</Question>
